#

Easy Garlic Herb Bread

25 min
$3.5
250 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

GlutenDairy

Dietary Tags:

Vegetarian

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Side Dish

Tags:

EasySide DishVegetarian

Description

Warm, buttery garlic bread infused with fresh herbs – the perfect side for any meal!

Ingredients

  • french bread: 1 loaf
  • unsalted butter: 1/2 cup
  • fresh parsley: 2 tablespoons, chopped
  • fresh basil: 2 tablespoons, chopped
  • garlic: 4 cloves, minced
  • salt: 1/2 teaspoon
  • black pepper: 1/4 teaspoon
